    <paragraphs>
        <title>Other input types</title>
    
        <p>There are other input types, such as for multiple choice questions or tables of inputs. You may also be asked to input lists or sets.
            <ul>
                <li>Sets are enclosed by curly brackets \( \{a,b,c\} \) is entered <c>{a,b,c}</c></li>
                <li>Lists are enclosed by square brackets \( [a,b,c] \) is entered <c>[a,b,c]</c></li>
            </ul>
        </p>

